A firm, LinkPro Consult Integrated Limited, has planned to hold a hybrid meeting today for students and parents seeking to explore foreign education but finding the university application process cumbersome. In a hybrid event tagged “KUA AFRICA”, the company would be presenting parents, students, professionals and agents in Nigeria with one-on-one networking with representatives from prestigious international institutions of higher learning in Ireland and Germany. The meeting would be held at a designated venue in Lagos with offer holders, prospective students and professionals in the ICT, management, hospitality and tourism sectors.